!!! THIS IS A JOKE DO NOT USE ME EVER !!!

  - html :
      - head :
          - title : this is a title
          - link !type text/css !href http://someplace.com
          - script !type text/javascript : |
              alert('hello world');
          - style : |
              div#content{
                color: #000;
              }
              .big {
                font-size: 200%;
              }
              
            
      - body : 
          - div #content :
              - p .big : this is some content

Should result in an output of: 

  <html>
    <head>
      <title>this is a title</title>
      <link type='text/css' href='http://someplace.com' />
      <script type='text/javascript'>
        alert('hello world');
      </script>
      <style>
        div#content{
          color: #000;
        }
        .big {
          font-size: 200%;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
      <div id='content'>
        <p class='big'>
          this is some content
        </p>
      </div>
    </body>
  </html>
